snippet.textDisplay:
I had a near death experience when a flash current took hold of me. When I tried to show lifeguards I need help, I noticed that they were chatting and not giving attention at all. I think that if I was there 10 more seconds I wouldn't made it. If I didn't get my Uncle's attention, nobody would've noticed. 2 years after there were 4 teens who drowed at the same place I was.
I am not scared of water and will go swim again, but I just want to say thank you for what you guys do.
